Define pAz 0.0     # Phase of Azero
Define Ap  0.63085 # Mod. of Aplus
Define pAp 0.14    # Phase of Aplus
Define Am  0.10969 # Mod. of Aminus
Define pAm 2.24    # Phase of Aminus (pi + 0.9035)
#
Alias      MyK*0       K*0
Alias      Myanti-K*0  anti-K*0
ChargeConj Myanti-K*0  MyK*0
# 
Decay B0sig
  1.000    MyK*0    Myanti-K*0   SVV_HELAMP Ap pAp Az pAz Am pAm;
Enddecay
Decay anti-B0sig
  1.000    Myanti-K*0    MyK*0   SVV_HELAMP Am pAm Az pAz Ap pAp;
Enddecay
#
Decay MyK*0
  1.000     K+    pi-            VSS;
Enddecay
